{"tid":1786434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冬至飯酒樓預訂好轉　業界擔心好消息來得太遲","createTime":"2019-12-17T06:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T08:47:38.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"007e8be6361b5c2b14a777d662de67290745db1c","tid":1786434,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=373654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D373654&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0j2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=e660cf5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D373654&h=5177bef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=373654</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】還有一星期就到冬至及聖誕，餐務管理協會表示，近日社會局勢較穩定，生意較前幾個月有好轉，冬至飯的預訂漸漸追回去年水平。但有主力做年輕人生意的party room負責人指，年輕人沒心情慶祝，預計聖誕生意額跌近六成。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冬至前這個周日，在太古的這間酒樓，晚市時間全場爆滿。這一個月催淚彈少了，市民都趁機會一家人吃飯舒舒氣。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所謂「冬大過年」，這間酒樓冬至飯的預訂數量已經追回和去年相若，但市民消費信心未恢復，套餐價格都不敢加價。<br />\n<br />\n楊位醒是餐務管理協會會長，他表示，在社會動盪情況下，這半年已有超過三百間酒樓結業。雖然年底訂檯情況有好轉，他擔心這個好消息來得太遲。<br />\n<br />\n有人歡喜有人愁，Simone是一間party room的老闆，生意有一半是來自年輕人。電腦上，往年排滿的預訂受到今年反修例運動影響，到現在仍然有不少空檔。<br />\n<br />\nSimon表示，生意不好的原因是受到反修例運動影響，年輕人都無心情在聖誕消費，生意只有去年的三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n老闆說聖誕節會有不少團體來開大型派對，因為人數眾多，都會打通房間讓他們使用，今年多是6至8人的小型派對，一間房已經夠用。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，社會問題非短時間可解決，對下年的生意不感樂觀。"},{"pid":"bf0665c0c03337b7e877fcb55653c8822cb6c4cb","tid":1786434,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e478ff360b46382f51e4ac2d98298c6c7c1a2e0","tid":1786434,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差1萬5千人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e5a3790644ea18ca26fd991560d156061b34997","tid":1786434,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}